{
  "book": 25,
  "chapter": 5,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "求耶和華垂憐"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Remember, O Lord, what has befallen us; Look, and see our reproach! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Remember, O Lord, what has befallen us; Look, and see our reproach!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our inheritance has been turned over to strangers, Our houses to aliens. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our inheritance has been turned over to strangers, Our houses to aliens."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We have become orphans without a father, Our mothers are like widows. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We have become orphans without a father, Our mothers are like widows."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We have to pay for our drinking water, Our wood comes to us at a price. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We have to pay for our drinking water, Our wood comes to us at a price."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our pursuers are at our necks; We are worn out, there is no rest for us. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our pursuers are at our necks; We are worn out, there is no rest for us."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We have submitted to Egypt and Assyria to get enough bread. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We have submitted to Egypt and Assyria to get enough bread."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our fathers sinned, and are no more; It is we who have borne their iniquities. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our fathers sinned, and are no more; It is we who have borne their iniquities."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Slaves rule over us; There is no one to deliver us from their hand. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Slaves rule over us; There is no one to deliver us from their hand."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We get our bread at the risk of our lives Because of the sword in the wilderness. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We get our bread at the risk of our lives Because of the sword in the wilderness."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our skin has become as hot as an oven, Because of the burning heat of famine. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our skin has become as hot as an oven, Because of the burning heat of famine."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They ravished the women in Zion, The virgins in the cities of Judah. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They ravished the women in Zion, The virgins in the cities of Judah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Princes were hung by their hands; Elders were not respected. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Princes were hung by their hands; Elders were not respected."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Young men worked at the grinding mill, And youths stumbled under loads of wood. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Young men worked at the grinding mill, And youths stumbled under loads of wood."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Elders are gone from the gate, Young men from their music. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Elders are gone from the gate, Young men from their music."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The joy of our hearts has ceased; Our dancing has been turned into mourning. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The joy of our hearts has ceased; Our dancing has been turned into mourning."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The crown has fallen from our head; Woe to us, for we have sinned! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The crown has fallen from our head; Woe to us, for we have sinned!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Because of this our heart is faint, Because of these things our eyes are dim; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Because of this our heart is faint, Because of these things our eyes are dim;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Because of Mount Zion which lies desolate, Foxes prowl in it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Because of Mount Zion which lies desolate, Foxes prowl in it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "You, O Lord, rule forever; Your throne is from generation to generation. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You, O Lord, rule forever; Your throne is from generation to generation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Why do You forget us forever? Why do You forsake us so long? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Why do You forget us forever? Why do You forsake us so long?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Restore us to You, O Lord, that we may be restored; Renew our days as of old, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Restore us to You, O Lord, that we may be restored; Renew our days as of old,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Restore us to You, O Lord, that we may be restored; Renew our days as of old,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Unless You have utterly rejected us And are exceedingly angry with us. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Unless You have utterly rejected us And are exceedingly angry with us."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}